495
00:47:20,641 --> 00:47:22,362
[SPEAKER_04]: Yeah, and then this can only be one minute.

496
00:47:23,043 --> 00:47:29,146
[SPEAKER_04]: Yeah, so there's a new law, so cars have to be four feet away from bikers, pedestrians,

497
00:47:30,174 --> 00:47:35,956
[SPEAKER_04]: you know, whatever, like, so it's a law that I like a lot in theory.

498
00:47:35,976 --> 00:47:44,880
