[SPEAKER_04]: And yeah, I think, you know, WOC, Medford, MBAC will probably be talking about this at city events and things like that.

501
00:48:08,589 --> 00:48:16,114
[SPEAKER_04]: But we can also, you know, mention it in our table or have something to make the public aware that this got passed.

502
00:48:16,194 --> 00:48:23,199
[SPEAKER_04]: And now it's actually the law to sort of, you know, keep yourself when you're driving four feet away from pedestrians and bikers.

503
