00:56:18,854 --> 00:56:19,975
[SPEAKER_06]: We don't have in Medford a

566
00:56:21,405 --> 00:56:25,228
[SPEAKER_06]: a system for this yet and we're looking into Arlington to see how this works.

567
00:56:26,128 --> 00:56:34,374
[SPEAKER_06]: So have you, Mark, have you actually gotten started with this program in Arlington?

568
00:56:34,394 --> 00:56:35,795
[SPEAKER_11]: Yeah, we have.

569
00:56:36,195 --> 00:56:41,779
[SPEAKER_11]: It's been going for like maybe two and a half months so far.

570
00:56:44,180 --> 00:56:48,983
[SPEAKER_11]: So the four of us were trained by a boat and

571
00:56:50,906 --> 00:56:51,527
[SPEAKER_11]: It was done.

572
00:56:52,087 --> 00:57:04,077
[SPEAKER_11]: So, um, Talia, our energy management person for the town got a grant from mass CDC to have the four of us trained and she got trained too.

573
00:57:05,038 --> 00:57:09,521
[SPEAKER_11]: Um, so, so we got trained that quote makes us quote coaches.

574
00:57:11,583 --> 00:57:20,070
[SPEAKER_11]: Um, so, so the four of us are, are the coaches for Arlington and, um, and we did an initial.

575
00:57:21,410 --> 00:57:25,713
[SPEAKER_11]: some initial publicity about it, both by web and email.

576
00:57:26,213 --> 00:57:32,737
[SPEAKER_11]: And we had an initial, what was it?

577
00:57:33,638 --> 00:57:38,080
[SPEAKER_11]: A presentation that we did at one of the schools in town.

578
00:57:38,801 --> 00:57:44,464
[SPEAKER_11]: And we had like maybe 50, 60 people there and then a bunch online for it.

579
00:57:46,386 --> 00:57:48,447
[SPEAKER_11]: And that generated a bunch of requests

580
00:57:49,803 --> 00:57:53,424
[SPEAKER_11]: So we've had lots of requests for help with getting heat pumps.

581
