587
00:58:37,504 --> 00:58:39,365
[SPEAKER_11]: And I haven't gotten to that point with anybody yet.

588
00:58:40,745 --> 00:58:45,988
[SPEAKER_11]: So I'd say it's taking maybe two hours per person so far or per household.

589
00:58:46,513 --> 00:58:49,776
