619
01:01:37,477 --> 01:01:37,617
[SPEAKER_11]: And

620
01:01:39,982 --> 01:01:42,864
[SPEAKER_11]: you know, I'll talk to them about the relative cost of it.

621
01:01:44,345 --> 01:01:46,086
[SPEAKER_11]: And, and there's always questions.

622
01:01:46,126 --> 01:01:47,447
[SPEAKER_11]: So every house is different.

623
01:01:48,627 --> 01:01:51,769
[SPEAKER_11]: And every house brings up new kinds of questions.

624
01:01:53,090 --> 01:01:54,111
[SPEAKER_11]: Sure, sure.

625
01:01:55,451 --> 01:01:56,152
[SPEAKER_08]: Thanks very much.

