01:06:54,844 --> 01:07:01,829
[SPEAKER_05]: We have the option of joining the city's consolidated electricity consumer plan.

687
01:07:03,350 --> 01:07:15,878
[SPEAKER_05]: And all of these things, you kind of have to look for each homeowner, as I'm sure you know better than I, each homeowner has to look at this whole constellation of choices.

688
01:07:16,918 --> 01:07:27,042
[SPEAKER_05]: in order to come to the best energy as a consumer, the best energy reduction package that they can do.

689
01:07:28,463 --> 01:07:34,465
[SPEAKER_05]: And so I'm just curious, are you as a coach advising them on all of that or?

690
01:07:34,485 --> 01:07:37,046
[SPEAKER_05]: A little bit.

691
01:07:38,187 --> 01:07:45,810
[SPEAKER_11]: So I will answer questions about most of these things, but I don't know a lot

