01:07:50,746 --> 01:07:55,648
[SPEAKER_05]: So you're focusing on the heat pump, whether heat pumps are a good idea for them.

693
01:07:55,668 --> 01:08:18,761
[SPEAKER_11]: I generally do ask them about putting up solar in conjunction with doing heat pumps saves you more money because the electricity used to heat pumps to run heat pumps is fairly expensive, especially

694
01:08:19,504 --> 01:08:25,088
