01:08:50,399 --> 01:08:55,981
[SPEAKER_11]: So running the electricity to run heat pumps is still fairly expensive.

704
01:08:58,682 --> 01:09:03,783
[SPEAKER_11]: And if you put PV on your roof, you can cover a lot of the costs through the PV.

705
01:09:05,464 --> 01:09:07,665
[SPEAKER_02]: So we generally do talk to people about that.

