01:10:19,751 --> 01:10:20,111
[SPEAKER_05]: No, no.

719
01:10:20,291 --> 01:10:27,676
[SPEAKER_05]: I'm talking about solar, rooftop solar would cover 70% of my power costs.

720
01:10:28,296 --> 01:10:29,557
