01:10:37,200 --> 01:10:38,880
[SPEAKER_11]: Well, no.

725
01:10:39,260 --> 01:10:43,481
[SPEAKER_11]: So, I mean, if you put in heat pumps, your house is going to require more.

726
01:10:45,221 --> 01:10:45,761
[SPEAKER_11]: That's right.

727
01:10:46,602 --> 01:10:47,102
[SPEAKER_05]: That's right.

728
01:10:47,122 --> 01:10:48,902
